# Build-context ignore for the MCP image (KAN-47). The build context is the REPO
# ROOT (docker build -f mcp/Dockerfile .), but the Dockerfile only COPYs mcp/ and
# its sibling kanban-client/ — so exclude everything else to keep the context tiny.
# BuildKit prefers this <dockerfile>.dockerignore over the root .dockerignore.
*
!kanban-client
!mcp

# Drop heavy/derived bits even inside the two dirs we keep.
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
